{"tid":1223933,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"理性討論而家既惡法一定要退回 但此法必定要修","createTime":"2019-06-15T00:11:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-15T07:24:08.000Z","uid":98232,"like":0,"dislike":28,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"df81d40c52ce9a52f65f9c97e39f8f81882b375b","tid":1223933,"uid":98232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T00:11:55.000Z","msg":"現時惡法得唔到香港人信任 <br />\n怕中國會以各種借口引渡政治犯人<br />\n其實就算無惡法 <br />\n中國一直以來都會洗頂艇咁捉人番中國<br />\n可以同政府商討 其實係直接同由一講數<br />\n因為就算林鄭下台 <br />\n係中國統治底下邊個上台都會推呢條法<br />\n引渡殺人犯 詐騙犯可以照引渡 <br />\n但有政治背景既犯人必須先經過香港法官審理<br />\n再進行判斷是否有需要移交中國<br />\n因為係反惡法既同事mk妹既死亦都要仲張正義<br />\n大粒墨亦不能夠逍遙法外"},{"pid":"67127784f11f1d77fb85c5f1582be07e19b7362e","tid":1223933,"uid":98232,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T00:14:43.000Z","msg":"我本人是反對現時此惡法 <br />\n應為法是有必要修 <br />\n但要設不破壞香港司法獨立前提底下去修<br />\n利申：12號有野餐"},{"pid":"d44e396c4274847b1db59620be56540d138ccec9","tid":1223933,"uid":98232,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T00:25:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44f725a866f98fb2e427b080d05b3b93dbcc58ed","tid":1223933,"uid":98232,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T00:25:49.000Z","msg":"正經野無人討論？"},{"pid":"414ab8c9fabb56ef8fa27cd46cce1fe605bbd608","tid":1223933,"uid":176802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T00:35:11.000Z","msg":"好 認真討論<br />\n邊個係由一<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"653cc5a8db191df957154e5781f1a9836c176fa7","tid":1223933,"uid":98232,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"414ab8c9fabb56ef8fa27cd46cce1fe605bbd608","tid":1223933,"uid":176802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T00:35:11.000Z","msg":"好 認真討論<br />\n邊個係由一<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T00:41:28.000Z","msg":"中國 我打殘打錯<br />\n因為要推此法係中共 <br />\n邊個上台都係會推<br />\n所以比壓力林鄭亦都係比壓力中共<br />\n政治現實係香港仲係中共統治<br />\n呢條法只會推遲唔會撒回<br />\n倒不如 直接同佢講數 <br />\n好似我上文咁講 有政治背景既人<br />\n要中國交哂所有罪証 <br />\n而由香港法官去判有無需要引渡<br />\n呢個只係我簡單既把關<br />\n當然如果覺得仲係唔夠可以再嚴格把關"},{"pid":"e868bcdfd0102f56f212f7dc56168a10f0686769","tid":1223933,"uid":98232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T03:19:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0deed102054458c6160f398cd3b58c689366882","tid":1223933,"uid":98232,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T03:34:30.000Z","msg":"入黎討論下 真心為香港好 <br />\n如果全撤咁大粒墨殺完人唔洗負責任？"},{"pid":"497c8c30f742a52dff5dd72e60d55dfe1ebd1271","tid":1223933,"uid":39297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f0deed102054458c6160f398cd3b58c689366882","tid":1223933,"uid":98232,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T03:34:30.000Z","msg":"入黎討論下 真心為香港好 <br />\n如果全撤咁大粒墨殺完人唔洗負責任？"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T03:38:18.000Z","msg":"屌你都廢事<br />\n台灣已經講咗唔會認受呀<br />\n修黎都唔會捉到佢呀<br />\n係咪文盲呀"},{"pid":"1677c9d1c3c05c512daa92238db6998fbc88f6a8","tid":1223933,"uid":133100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"497c8c30f742a52dff5dd72e60d55dfe1ebd1271","tid":1223933,"uid":39297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f0deed102054458c6160f398cd3b58c689366882","tid":1223933,"uid":98232,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T03:34:30.000Z","msg":"入黎討論下 真心為香港好 <br />\n如果全撤咁大粒墨殺完人唔洗負責任？"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T03:38:18.000Z","msg":"屌你都廢事<br />\n台灣已經講咗唔會認受呀<br />\n修黎都唔會捉到佢呀<br />\n係咪文盲呀"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T03:39:27.000Z","msg":"oh, 討論完咗"},{"pid":"1cde054e7ec05a88aaef1eb9921d6e2b4a6a3604","tid":1223933,"uid":98232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"497c8c30f742a52dff5dd72e60d55dfe1ebd1271","tid":1223933,"uid":39297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f0deed102054458c6160f398cd3b58c689366882","tid":1223933,"ui